  "description": "<p><strong>Role: Assistant Site Leader/Service Engineer (ACMV, Electrical, Mechanical)</strong></p><p><strong>Industry: Facilities services / Energy</strong></p><p><strong>Location: Islandwide</strong></p><p><strong>5.5 days | Mon-Fri: 9am to 6pm </strong></p><p><strong>Salary: $2500 - $4000</strong><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ol><li><strong>Diploma in Engineering/Sustainability/Building fields or relevant work experience</strong></li><li><strong>Able to perform shifts work.</strong></li></ol><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>To implement a maintenance regime for site equipment to keep the equipment functioning at the required plant and airside efficiency</li><li>Troubleshoot technical issues and thereafter organize and carry out the necessary repair works</li><li>Schedule, plan and assign the monthly duties of the team</li><li>Conduct skills training to new team members</li><li>Maintain a high degree of safety standards and create a safety conscious workplace</li><li>Conduct daily toolbox meetings Customer Service and Management</li><li>Attend discussions and meetings with building management and tenants</li><li>Prepare proposals/quotations and routine service reports</li><li>Attend to and resolve technical faults withing the committed timeline</li><li>Audit and maintain high consistency of work methods and work quality delivered by the team</li></ul><p>Tai Jia Seng Reg No: R26159755</p><p>The Supreme Hr Advisory Pte Ltd EA No: 14C7279</p>",
